  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you can make a melee&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Touch-Attacks\">touch attack</a>&nbsp;as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>&nbsp;that inflicts 1d4 points of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Nonlethal-Damage\">nonlethal damage</a>&nbsp;+ 1 for every two sorcerer levels you possess. In addition, the target is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Dazzled\">dazzled</a>&nbsp;for 1 minute. Creatures with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Low-Light-Vision\">low-light vision</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Darkvision\">darkvision</a>&nbsp;are not&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Dazzled\">dazzled</a>&nbsp;by this ability. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>",
